title: Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Promenade Bike Trail and Bicycle Storage', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
